        <note>Mistakes blotched out with black; written without daṇḍas; final folio (f. 22) badly damaged.</note>
        <note>Incipit: śrīgurubhyo namaḥ śrīgaṇeṣāya namaḥ nārada uvāca yas tuṣṭādau tvayā nātha munisiddhair anekadhā anekaśāstramaryādā kathitā parameśvara 1 prasanno bhava deveśa bhavaduḥkhavināśana anekaśāstrabhramaṇād asmākaṁ mohitaṁ manaḥ 2 etac ca kāraṇaṁ kiṁcit kiṁ yogaḥ procyate śrutau yogaṁ ca ṣadvidhaṁ proktaṁ nānā tvaṁ tasya dṛśyate 3 (f. 1v).</note>
        <note>Explicit: āsanādikrameṇaiva prāṇāyāmaṁ samabhyaset abhyāsāc ca svayaṁ prājño gacchate vyomamaṁḍalaṁ ayaṁ yogaḥ sarvaśāstreṣu vijānīyād varānane guroḥ prasādāt jñātavyaṁ rahasyam akulāgamaṁ 23 (f.22v).</note>
