              </respStmt>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīakulāgame mahātaṁtre yogasārasamuccaye mahādevapārvatīsaṁvāde navamaḥ paṭalaḥ saṁpūrṇaṃ śrīsītāḥ (f. 22v).</colophon>
